<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.9">
<l>kaṇṭa kaṭalum malaiyu mulakēḻum</l>
<l>muṇṭattuk kāṟṟā mukilvaṇṇā vōveṉ</l>
<l>ṟiṇṭaic caṭaimuṭi yīca ṉirakkoḷḷa</l>
<l>maṇṭai niṟaittāṉē yaccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">mārvil maṟuvaṉē yaccōvaccō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who filled [his] begging bowl when Śiva</l>
<l rend="indent">with a crown of matted locks and garlands</l>
<l>[came] to beg for himself, saying</l>
<l rend="indent">“O cloud-hued One, the oceans that can be seen,</l>
<l rend="indent">mountains, and all the seven worlds do not</l>
<l rend="indent">assuage [the hunger] of [my] skull bowl,”</l>
<l>Oh! Oh! He with the mark on [His] chest! Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
